Author: FeatherWorld
Text: That's why I don't have it. I can't trust myself and when I do, I end up eating too much and get cravings throughout the day and usually overeat by the end. I miss it so much.

Author: ComplexCrab
Text: I just woke up and I'm dreading breakfast too. Lying in bed debating whether I should eat or go back to bed or find something distracting to do for the next couple hours while I listen to my stomach grumble..
